Controller - Class in es.upm.gib.eutilsrdfwrapper
This class offers the public programmatic interface for launching queries to NCBI2RDF

Queries can be of two types: - SPARQL: in the form of a String - ConceptsQuery: a self-defined non-standard object that represents a query to this software.
